cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with visual categorization, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of multiple features and efficient part detection also suggests a machine learning approach (cs.LG, cs.AI). The mention of automatic segmentation and the use of off-the-shelf recognition pipeline suggests a multimedia approach (cs.MM). Finally, the use of mean average precision as a performance metric suggests information retrieval (cs.IR).
